'''Banks''' is an incarcerated man who was learning to fight fires.

==History==
Banks is an incarcerated man who was in a program to train him to fight wildfires and assist firefighters. He asked a lot of questions during this process. At the end of the training, Sullivan said he'd make an excellent firefighter.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
He has a cousin who is a firefighter at station 23.
